    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p><p>Top, tail, peel and slice your <strong>carrot[s]</strong> into discs on the diagonal, then slice each individual <strong>carrot disc</strong> into matchsticks</p><p>Wash then cut your<strong> pak choi </strong>in half, separating the <strong>white base</strong> and <strong>green tops</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and chop the into bite-sized pieces</p>",
