            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine<strong> </strong>your <strong>sambal paste</strong> with your <strong>ketjap manis</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>tomato ketchup </strong>and <strong>toasted sesame oil </strong>in a bowl with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>mie goreng sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
