            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>chopped pak choi green tops</strong>, <strong>drained noodles </strong>and <strong>mie goreng sauce</strong> to the pan with the vegetables and mix it all together until everything coated in the sauce – this is your <strong>vegetable mie goreng</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy noodle water<strong> </strong>if your sauce is looking a little dry!</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
