            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1723202057723-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>vegetable mie goreng</strong> and top with a <strong>fried egg</strong></p><p>Drizzle over your <strong>sriracha </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and garnish with the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
